metadata.name: ~ SilkWay ~ Book is a great way to start the day
metadata.description:
The ancient Silk Road, founded in the 2nd century BC, connected entire civilizations. It got its name because of the silk that was transported by caravans from China to the West. But, in addition to the unique fabric, it was of great importance in the exchange of not only goods, but also knowledge, culture and other things, which had a great influence on history.

This collection is not historically accurate. This is an attempt to convey the atmosphere and mood of that period of time, through the prism of the life of ordinary people and their history.

Made with AI+Photoshop  
3000x1714 px  
300dpi
